{
  "stem": "20405.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after they make the holes and everything else, they took us-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] no, they took us-- yeah, they-- they took us to inside the Birkenau to the regular barracks.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were [INAUDIBLE] over the crematoriums working.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we-- we put us-- they put us in one barrack, inside.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they locked up the doors.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, over there we were a few Greeks and few Polands-- all the ones working in the crematoriums.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, we were thinking that they locked us over here because they're gonna killed us now.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They don't need us anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the meantime, we saw some flames at the entrance of the-- of Birkenau, some flames.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was all the-- the papers they had over there, the officers and so on-- everything on flame.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At the other side, we saw for a-- from a window that too many kids, children with with no numbers on it, walking and getting out.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And some other sick people-- they couldn't kill them, because they didn't want to kill them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They couldn't kill them, because the Russian was so near, they didn't want to leave bodies on the-- on the side, to let the Russians see all those-- all those bodies, something unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So now we are in the barrack.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we saw everybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was almost night.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody going out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Before they-- they're hanging us over there, locked up over here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The Greek people, again, just broke the doors, as we say, and get out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Poland was afraid-- they're going to kill us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But anyway, they're going to killed us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because they didn't want to leave anybody working in the Sonderkommando to be alive, just to test-- testify, like I'm testifying now.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That was the idea of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
